                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-310-off1636 t18280221-310-cd1637"></join>, 10lbs. weight of quicksilver, value 25s., and 1 lb. weight of gamboge, value 7s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
